ZCUSTOMER: Customer master table.

Fields: CustomerID, Name, Address, Contact, etc.

ZPROJECT: Projects table.

Fields: ProjectID, CustomerID (foreign key), ProjectName, StartDate, EndDate, Status.

ZBILLING: Billing header table.

Fields: BillingID, ProjectID, BillingDate, TotalAmount, Status.

ZBILLING_ITEMS: Billing details table.

Fields: BillingItemID, BillingID (foreign key), Description, Amount, Tax.

Data Dictionary (DDIC) Considerations:
Use appropriate data elements, domains, and foreign key relationships.

Consider using views (e.g., join ZPROJECT and ZCUSTOMER) for reporting purposes.

